_sText:
Surf_the_dawning by Clemm

Original idea by Roosta, who made Surf_the_gloaming


After playing Roosta's epic map, I decided it was time
to make a sister-like map, although I could never make
a map as epic as the gloaming.

This map is a intermediate-advanced level surf, but not
skill surf.  You'll notice a lot of gloaming features here,
all credit goes to Roosta for original idea.

***This is the beta version, your feedback will help me
help you with how the final version will turn out***

Made and played for 66 tick servers ONLY

This map wouldn't have been possible had it not been for 
the following people:
